t it go: my heart shall not reproach me so long as I live.","year":-1520},{"id":"recyjixAUwkDPHN94","ref":"Job.27.7","text":"Let mine enemy be as the wicked, and he that riseth up against me as the unrighteous.","year":-1520},{"id":"reciHY7qGDGD4fwK2","ref":"Job.27.8","text":"For what is the hope of the hypocrite, though he hath gained, when God taketh away his soul?","year":-1520}]}
